Description:
You come across a large airship. Nezglekt steps forward as he waves to another squid head emerging from the deck of the ship and invites you aboard.

He explains to you that he serves on this ship under the command of Captain Tsnemo, then introduces you to him and Tsnemo says:

"Pleased to meet Nezglekt's companions, I am Tsnemo, captain of this merchant ship.
DescriptionAction: What brings you here? Anything specific you want to report to me Nezglekt?
